Utako Nakayasu: Tisch School of the Arts at NYU                           Skip to content        Performance Studies About the Program Admissions BA Program MA Program PhD Program Course Offerings Admin & Faculty Students Alumni PS Spotlights  News & Events Projects & Publications Blog Facebook  home > Performance Studies              Biography of       Utako Nakayasu  Performance Studies   Utako Nakayasu MA in Performance Studies, New York University  Education BA in Theater, CUNY Brooklyn College     Academic Interests Gender Performativity, Theater Anthropology, Performance in ritual, religion, fictional characters. Biography Utako is from Japan. She was a member of Takarazuka Revue Company. Takarazuka Revue is a popular musical company in Japan and consists of only female performers. She mainly played male roles. Takarazuka has various performance genres, including musicals and dance shows. The repertoire covers both Japanese and western titles. (more about Takarazuka Revue: http://kageki.hankyu.co.jp/english/) She left Takarazuka Revue in 2005 and came to NY to study at Stony Brook University in 2006. She believes herself as an actor rather than a singer or a dancer. She will be back on stage when her academic desire is satisfied. She is a material girl, but loves animals and nature! Her dream is having a wedding at Cinderella’s castle. Biography Utako is from Japan. She was a member of Takarazuka Revue Company. Takarazuka Revue is a popular musical company in Japan and consists of only female performers. She mainly played male roles. Takarazuka has various performance genres, including musicals and dance shows. The repertoire covers both Japanese and western titles. (more about Takarazuka Revue: http://kageki.hankyu.co.jp/english/) She left Takarazuka Revue in 2005 and came to NY to study at Stony Brook University in 2006. She believes herself as an actor rather than a singer or a dancer. She will be back on stage when her academic desire is satisfied. She is a material girl, but loves animals and nature! Her dream is having a wedding at Cinderella’s castle.
